1
00:00:41,332 --> 00:00:42,542
Jadi…

2
00:00:46,629 --> 00:00:48,548
Jangan cakap apa-apa dulu.

3
00:00:50,675 --> 00:00:54,345
<i>Aku tak boleh kata ini kesilapan</i>
<i>dan kami patut pura-pura…</i>

4
00:00:57,849 --> 00:00:59,434
<i>ia tak pernah berlaku.</i>

5
00:01:08,485 --> 00:01:10,487
<i>Sebab ini bukan kesilapan.</i>

6
00:01:20,497 --> 00:01:21,498
Dah sampai.

7
00:01:28,421 --> 00:01:29,464
Tunggu dulu.

8
00:01:33,635 --> 00:01:36,971
Nah. Esok hari terakhir pameran ini.

9
00:01:46,106 --> 00:01:47,190
Saya tunggu.

10
00:01:53,947 --> 00:01:54,906
Saya balik dulu.

11
00:01:57,826 --> 00:01:58,660
Okey.

12
00:03:18,114 --> 00:03:20,783
PAMERAN SOLO LEE KYU-TAE

13
00:03:31,544 --> 00:03:34,172
PAMERAN SOLO LEE KYU-TAE

14
00:05:15,481 --> 00:05:17,483
Tunggu situ. Saya datang.

15
00:05:37,795 --> 00:05:38,796
Maaflah lambat.

16
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,298
Tak apa, jangan risau.

17
00:05:43,551 --> 00:05:44,469
Itu…

18
00:05:46,471 --> 00:05:48,222
Cepatlah. Nanti kita lambat.

19
00:05:49,515 --> 00:05:50,350
Okey.

20
00:06:02,278 --> 00:06:03,613
Kenapa awak lambat?

21
00:06:04,989 --> 00:06:06,324
Yang penting saya datang.

22
00:06:07,617 --> 00:06:08,785
Kenapa awak datang?

23
00:06:10,203 --> 00:06:11,788
EPISOD 9
SUKA ATAU CINTA

24
00:06:11,871 --> 00:06:13,289
Sebab nak jumpa awaklah.

25
00:06:24,801 --> 00:06:25,718
Awak okey?

26
00:06:27,428 --> 00:06:29,514
Ya. Mestilah okey.

27
00:06:43,444 --> 00:06:44,529
Minum.

28
00:06:50,910 --> 00:06:51,911
Saya jaga awak.

29
00:07:13,015 --> 00:07:14,267
Kuning? Betulkah?

30
00:07:15,017 --> 00:07:15,852
Cantiknya!

31
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,106
Tukar gaya, okey?

32
00:07:20,189 --> 00:07:21,107
Rapat sikit.

33
00:07:33,828 --> 00:07:35,621
Tengoklah! Saya pandai, bukan?

34
00:07:44,005 --> 00:07:45,089
Awak okey?

35
00:07:45,173 --> 00:07:46,674
- Saya boleh.
- Betul?

36
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:53,389
Kita berlima, jadi tambah tiga lauk.

37
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:54,891
- Betul.
- Dua jenis mi.

38
00:07:54,974 --> 00:07:57,393
- Keju. Tambah dua.
- Suun.

39
00:07:57,477 --> 00:08:00,563
Pesan mi <i>jjolmyeon </i>juga, dengan ladu.

40
00:08:00,646 --> 00:08:01,981
- Betul.
- Sedapnya!

41
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:04,525
Jom makan berdua.

42
00:08:05,568 --> 00:08:06,569
Menarik.

43
00:08:09,363 --> 00:08:10,698
Nah!

44
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:13,493
Okey. Suka tak?

45
00:08:14,368 --> 00:08:15,786
Comelnya.

46
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,376
Macam mana? Sedap tak?

47
00:08:25,213 --> 00:08:26,547
Sedap.

48
00:08:27,757 --> 00:08:29,342
Saya nak rasa satulah.

49
00:08:29,425 --> 00:08:33,095
Cuba rasa kutlet dulu. Jangan…

50
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,232
Masinnya. Awak okey tak?

51
00:08:44,315 --> 00:08:46,317
- Saya suka. Betul.
- Jangan makan.

52
00:08:53,199 --> 00:08:54,200
Mesti sedap.

53
00:09:08,631 --> 00:09:09,507
Terima kasih.

54
00:09:10,007 --> 00:09:11,551
Biar saya tuangkan.

55
00:09:20,309 --> 00:09:21,978
Dua penutup untuk dua botol!

56
00:09:23,104 --> 00:09:25,106
- Saya boleh minum segelas.
- Jangan.

57
00:10:12,111 --> 00:10:16,490
Ya, tengah hari tadi,
saya makan <i>gimbap </i>tuna dan mi.

58
00:10:16,574 --> 00:10:17,408
Tangan saya?

59
00:10:17,992 --> 00:10:21,746
Tak sakit macam semalam,
tapi belum baik betul-betul.

60
00:10:22,371 --> 00:10:25,249
Okey. Nanti saya telefon lagi.

61
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:31,714
Dia telefon 10 kali sehari.
Awak tak kisah dengar kami borak, bukan?

62
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,174
Tak kisah.

63
00:10:33,257 --> 00:10:34,925
Dia duduk jauh sekarang.

64
00:10:37,678 --> 00:10:40,097
- Apa?
- Awak nampak gembira, itu saja.

65
00:10:41,182 --> 00:10:42,850
Gembira? Betulkah?

66
00:10:47,271 --> 00:10:49,523
Okeylah, saya nak pergi siapkan.

67
00:10:53,903 --> 00:10:54,737
ULASAN TEMA KE-46

68
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:58,115
<i>Kami berjaya keluar</i>
<i>tanpa disedari pengurusnya,</i>

69
00:10:58,199 --> 00:10:59,992
<i>tapi peminatnya ada mana-mana.</i>

70
00:11:00,076 --> 00:11:02,411
<i>Aku pegang tangannya dan lari.</i>

71
00:11:02,495 --> 00:11:05,706
<i>Tapi tempat letak kereta pun</i>
<i>dipenuhi para peminatnya,</i>

72
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:09,877
<i>jadi kami menyorok</i>
<i>di antara van dan tembok.</i>

73
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,797
<i>- Aku dengar degupan jantungnya.</i>
- Wah.

74
00:11:13,297 --> 00:11:15,800
<i>Aku turut rasa kehangatan tubuhnya.</i>

75
00:11:16,425 --> 00:11:17,426
<i>Kemudian…</i>

76
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:19,178
Gilalah.

77
00:11:24,642 --> 00:11:27,311
PINTU MASUK UTAMA
DEWAN KONSERT DU

78
00:11:35,069 --> 00:11:36,445
Di sini jugakah?

79
00:11:38,531 --> 00:11:40,658
Kenapa? Ada masalah?

80
00:11:41,575 --> 00:11:43,327
Tak. Tak ada masalah.

81
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:58,551
Nanti, sayang. Kalau pengurus datang…

82
00:11:59,051 --> 00:11:59,885
Diam saja.

83
00:12:00,469 --> 00:12:01,929
Okey.

84
00:12:05,099 --> 00:12:06,434
Jangan gerak.

85
00:12:25,077 --> 00:12:26,162
Tunggu dulu.

86
00:12:26,245 --> 00:12:28,164
Awak nak tukar tema lagi?

87
00:12:29,665 --> 00:12:30,875
Ya.

88
00:12:30,958 --> 00:12:32,710
Sabar-sabar sikit.

89
00:12:32,793 --> 00:12:37,381
Cuba 10 tema seminggu dulu.

90
00:12:37,465 --> 00:12:39,467
Kenapa? Saya banyak masa lapang.

91
00:12:41,218 --> 00:12:44,054
Kalau laju-laju begini,

92
00:12:44,138 --> 00:12:47,725
bulan depan dah habislah
900 calon awak jumpa.

93
00:12:47,808 --> 00:12:49,560
Tapi

94
00:12:50,144 --> 00:12:51,979
saya suka tempat ini.

95
00:12:53,063 --> 00:12:54,064
Itu dah jelas.

96
00:12:54,148 --> 00:12:58,277
Saya rasa gembira bukan main.
Keyakinan saya melambung tinggi.

97
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,362
Saya tak dituduh gila jantan

98
00:13:00,446 --> 00:13:03,407
atau dipandang serong
kerana tak serius bercinta.

99
00:13:03,491 --> 00:13:05,242
Saya boleh tukar-tukar pakwe.

100
00:13:06,744 --> 00:13:07,745
Bukan itu saja,

101
00:13:07,828 --> 00:13:11,248
apabila saya cuba tema
yang semua orang rasa susah,

102
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:14,585
saya boleh habiskan sekali jalan.

103
00:13:15,252 --> 00:13:17,963
Saya suka betul perasaan ini.

104
00:13:18,839 --> 00:13:21,258
Kehebatan saya tak boleh disangkal.

105
00:13:21,926 --> 00:13:23,427
Puas hati betul!

106
00:13:25,054 --> 00:13:26,055
RATING JANJI TEMU

107
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:27,431
Hantar.

108
00:13:27,515 --> 00:13:28,432
Okey.

109
00:13:31,811 --> 00:13:35,272
ULASAN TEMA KE-178
"JIRAN SEBELAH"

110
00:13:35,815 --> 00:13:37,983
592 ORANG SUKA, 930 KOMEN

111
00:13:38,567 --> 00:13:41,320
Apa ini? Kenapa banyak sangat komen?

112
00:13:41,821 --> 00:13:43,823
SIARAN ANDA MENCECAH 10,000 PAPARAN!

113
00:13:47,785 --> 00:13:49,537
<i>Siaran anda mencecah 10,000 paparan!</i>

114
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:52,456
Eh, apa dah jadi?

115
00:13:52,998 --> 00:13:55,167
NAEMO

116
00:13:57,336 --> 00:14:00,798
Siapa hias pokok ini? Bila dia hias?

117
00:14:01,841 --> 00:14:02,883
Saya pun pelik.

118
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:04,593
Cuti Seollal nanti, buat apa?

119
00:14:05,886 --> 00:14:08,848
Saya? Makan limau dan baca komik.

120
00:14:09,807 --> 00:14:12,643
Ibu saya tak kasi datang,
dia nak pergi bercuti.

121
00:14:12,726 --> 00:14:16,230
Nampaknya saya memerap sajalah
di rumah sampai lima hari.

122
00:14:16,313 --> 00:14:18,816
Baguslah, ambil peluang berehat.

123
00:14:23,696 --> 00:14:25,364
Dia kata nak tolong kita.

124
00:14:27,575 --> 00:14:31,328
Nanti saya letak pokok di stor.
Kemas yang ini dulu?

125
00:14:31,412 --> 00:14:32,246
Ya.

126
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,542
Cuti nanti, awak buat apa?

127
00:14:36,625 --> 00:14:38,919
Saya nak baca komik dan makan limau.

128
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,046
Apa?

129
00:14:52,057 --> 00:14:53,309
Kamu berdua…

130
00:14:57,688 --> 00:15:01,108
Apa saya nak buat
dengan kaki komik macam kamu?

131
00:15:01,817 --> 00:15:04,820
Ini zaman strimlah,
tapi kamu masih baca buku komik?

132
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:08,324
Sebab kamulah En. Hwang asyik kata
saya buta komik.

133
00:15:08,407 --> 00:15:11,118
Berhentilah baca komik. Cukup-cukuplah.

134
00:15:12,161 --> 00:15:14,830
Saya nak pergi simpan barang di arkib.

135
00:15:26,592 --> 00:15:28,510
Bahaya betul di luar sana.

136
00:15:32,556 --> 00:15:34,725
Kenapa ikut saya? Mana boleh!

137
00:15:34,808 --> 00:15:37,144
Kenapa? Saya cuma nak simpan barang.

138
00:15:37,227 --> 00:15:39,396
Hei! Okey, saya keluar dululah.

139
00:15:51,951 --> 00:15:52,952
Tunggu sekejap.

140
00:16:06,006 --> 00:16:08,634
- Kalau ada orang nampak?
- Buat macam biasa.

141
00:16:08,717 --> 00:16:10,219
Cakap senanglah.

142
00:16:11,303 --> 00:16:13,639
Saya tak pandai menipu.

143
00:16:14,139 --> 00:16:15,975
Stres betul aku di pejabat ini.

144
00:16:19,603 --> 00:16:20,938
Jom kantoi terus, nak?

145
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:23,482
Awak gila.

146
00:16:45,838 --> 00:16:46,922
<i>Sayang.</i>

147
00:16:50,801 --> 00:16:52,720
- Awak okey?
- Apa?

148
00:16:55,889 --> 00:16:56,724
Saya okey.

149
00:17:05,774 --> 00:17:07,443
<i>Seronok kacau saya, ya?</i>

150
00:17:08,027 --> 00:17:09,236
<i>Makan apa malam ini?</i>

151
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:13,282
<i>Saya kena jumpa Cik Yun.</i>
<i>Makanlah tanpa saya.</i>

152
00:17:14,658 --> 00:17:16,243
<i>Nanti saya jemput awak.</i>

153
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:27,921
Pesan makanan untuk saya.

154
00:17:28,005 --> 00:17:30,466
Aduh, sakitnya tangan saya!

155
00:17:30,966 --> 00:17:33,886
Industri ini kerjakan penulis macam hamba.

156
00:17:33,969 --> 00:17:36,638
Saya nak minta kurangkan lukisan
dalam kontrak baru.

157
00:17:37,139 --> 00:17:39,516
Nanti nak pegang sudu pun tak larat.

158
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,769
Kontrak Yun Song dah nak tamat.

159
00:17:41,852 --> 00:17:44,813
Susahlah nak sambung kontrak
dengan syarat yang memuaskan.

160
00:17:46,774 --> 00:17:50,611
Awak dah tanya En. Hwang
tentang kontrak baru?

161
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:54,490
Tak. Dia belum cakap apa-apa pun lagi.

162
00:17:55,282 --> 00:17:56,283
Nanti agaknya.

163
00:18:07,252 --> 00:18:10,506
Kalau kita tunggu musim depan,
itu dah lambat sangat.

164
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:12,758
Awak ada idea?

165
00:18:14,468 --> 00:18:18,305
Ingat lagi semasa <i>PlanC</i>
dapat slot Jumaat macam kita?

166
00:18:18,388 --> 00:18:22,559
Mari kita kaji apa yang tak kena
dan buat perubahan macam masa itu.

167
00:18:23,268 --> 00:18:25,813
Awak dah tak ada pilihan lain.

168
00:18:25,896 --> 00:18:28,649
Mesti ada sesuatu
yang awak saja boleh buat.

169
00:18:28,732 --> 00:18:29,566
Seo.

170
00:18:30,442 --> 00:18:31,985
Awak nak lepas tangan, ya?

171
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:36,281
Tak, saya pun akan buat
kerja saya sebaik mungkin.

172
00:18:36,782 --> 00:18:41,411
Tapi jangan lupa yang ini komik awak.

173
00:18:51,505 --> 00:18:54,466
Saya pun dah tak tahulah. Pening kepala.

174
00:18:56,885 --> 00:18:58,303
Boleh saya tengok?

175
00:18:59,388 --> 00:19:00,222
Okey.

176
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:06,228
DIA YANG PERLU DIKENAL
RANGKA CERITA

177
00:19:07,396 --> 00:19:08,397
Awak rasa?

178
00:19:09,231 --> 00:19:11,733
Mungkin pembaca tertarik sekejap tapi…

179
00:19:12,651 --> 00:19:13,652
Tapi itu sajalah?

180
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:16,280
Ya.

181
00:19:18,407 --> 00:19:20,075
Ini tak boleh jadi.

182
00:19:21,702 --> 00:19:24,329
Kami kena cari jalan
kalau nak kalahkan <i>PlanC</i>.

183
00:19:25,622 --> 00:19:28,458
Cukuplah, pesaing tak boleh
tengok lebih-lebih.

184
00:19:32,296 --> 00:19:33,130
Comel.

185
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,424
Apa?

186
00:19:36,341 --> 00:19:37,176
Taklah…

187
00:19:38,177 --> 00:19:39,428
Kenapa comel sangat?

188
00:19:42,055 --> 00:19:45,475
Eh, jangan nak comel-comel.
Orang serius buat kerja, tahu?

189
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:47,060
Eh?

190
00:19:57,571 --> 00:20:01,158
Saya nak lukisan yang macam
awak lukis untuk Hwany, boleh?

191
00:20:01,241 --> 00:20:02,075
Boleh.

192
00:20:02,159 --> 00:20:04,161
Betul? Tak tipu?

193
00:20:04,244 --> 00:20:05,078
Betul.

194
00:20:06,747 --> 00:20:08,749
Awak nak saya lukis awak?

195
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,084
Apa?

196
00:20:13,503 --> 00:20:14,755
Nak saya lukis awak?

197
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:21,094
Awak tak suka?

198
00:20:23,555 --> 00:20:24,973
Tak, saya suka.

199
00:20:36,568 --> 00:20:38,904
Awak dah tak ada pilihan lain.

200
00:20:38,987 --> 00:20:41,531
Mesti ada sesuatu
yang awak saja boleh buat.

201
00:20:47,871 --> 00:20:49,122
Geramnya…

202
00:20:49,665 --> 00:20:54,086
Kenapa semua orang asyik marah aku?
Serabut betullah…

203
00:21:03,345 --> 00:21:06,431
Kenapa semua orang asyik marah saya?

204
00:21:07,266 --> 00:21:10,811
Asal ada mulut,
semua tahu nak maki penulis saja!

205
00:21:10,894 --> 00:21:12,271
Mereka cakap senanglah!

206
00:21:12,354 --> 00:21:13,981
Cuba mereka lukis sendiri,

207
00:21:14,064 --> 00:21:16,650
jangan kata tiga panel, satu pun tak siap.

208
00:21:16,733 --> 00:21:18,151
Tahu nak mengarah saja.

209
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:22,531
Buat kerja laju, dikatanya cincai.
Buat elok-elok, dikatanya lembab.

210
00:21:22,614 --> 00:21:25,701
Semua tak kena! Sakit hati saya!

211
00:21:37,546 --> 00:21:38,964
Habis, nak tangguh lagi?

212
00:21:39,881 --> 00:21:42,801
Tak boleh. Saya kena siapkan.

213
00:21:44,219 --> 00:21:46,471
Sebab awak tak nak susahkan penerbit?

214
00:21:47,306 --> 00:21:48,974
Bukan begitu, tapi…

215
00:21:49,725 --> 00:21:52,811
Entahlah, saya cuma tak nak kecewakan dia.

216
00:21:54,563 --> 00:21:56,481
Kenapa? Sebab dia kawan awak?

217
00:21:59,359 --> 00:22:02,654
Awak memang baik hati, Song.

218
00:22:03,363 --> 00:22:07,117
Awak saja yang pernah kata saya baik.

219
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,369
Mereka bukannya tahu apa pun.

220
00:22:10,746 --> 00:22:11,705
Saya kena pergi.

221
00:22:12,289 --> 00:22:13,749
Nak pergi mana?

222
00:22:13,832 --> 00:22:16,335
Kerja rajin-rajin. Jangan hampakan kawan.

223
00:22:16,418 --> 00:22:18,670
Saya akan tolong beri semangat.

224
00:22:19,629 --> 00:22:22,049
Datang ke tempat kerja saya nanti.

225
00:22:30,140 --> 00:22:32,517
Apa hal? Dia yang suruh datang sini.

226
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:21,316
Wah!

227
00:23:23,819 --> 00:23:24,653
Awak datang.

228
00:23:26,238 --> 00:23:28,949
Ini apa? Cerita <i>Hansel dan Gretel</i>?

229
00:23:31,076 --> 00:23:34,287
Kalau rasa sedih,
ubatnya cuma makanan manis.

230
00:23:35,414 --> 00:23:36,832
Berkesan nampaknya.

231
00:24:02,274 --> 00:24:04,276
RESTORAN TAUHU BUATAN TANGAN

232
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:10,574
Kenapa mamat ini sibuk nak ikut
pasukan kita keluar makan?

233
00:24:14,119 --> 00:24:17,247
Naemo syarikat kecil.
Kita semua satu pasukan.

234
00:24:17,330 --> 00:24:19,416
Ya, betullah.

235
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:23,795
<i>Cinta yang anda impikan…</i>

236
00:24:23,879 --> 00:24:25,380
