PERASAAN PUN JADI PRODUK

464
00:43:48,834 --> 00:43:50,961
PENULIS DIKECAM KERANA MELANGGAN

465
00:43:51,795 --> 00:43:54,465
<i>Kadar kelahiran kita rendah.</i>
<i>Ini dah melampau.</i>

466
00:43:54,548 --> 00:43:56,383
<i>Apa kaitan kadar kelahiran?</i>

467
00:43:56,467 --> 00:44:00,429
<i>Ia memberi wanita harapan palsu</i>
<i>sampai tak pandang lelaki sebenar.</i>

468
00:44:00,512 --> 00:44:04,808
<i>Yuran langganannya tinggi.</i>
<i>Ramai orang muda terpaksa berhutang.</i>

469
00:44:04,892 --> 00:44:08,103
<i>Macam mana kau bayar? Pakai duit mak ayah?</i>

470
00:44:08,187 --> 00:44:10,105
<i>- Sedih aku dengar.</i>
- Sedih?

471
00:44:10,189 --> 00:44:13,150
<i>Main-main di dunia maya.</i>
<i>Sampah punya perempuan.</i>

472
00:44:13,233 --> 00:44:14,318
Sampah?

473
00:44:16,779 --> 00:44:18,614
Kau orang memang celaka!

474
00:44:20,449 --> 00:44:21,283
Mana dia?

475
00:44:22,743 --> 00:44:23,577
Saya tak tahu.

476
00:44:24,244 --> 00:44:27,498
Saya tunggu dia datang,
tapi dia tak muncul-muncul.

477
00:44:28,666 --> 00:44:30,417
Apa kita nak buat?

478
00:44:31,251 --> 00:44:33,754
Jangan risau. Biar saya masuk dulu.

479
00:44:59,822 --> 00:45:03,742
Biar betul?
Ini pakwe yang dia banggakan dulu?

480
00:45:03,826 --> 00:45:05,160
Tak sangka…

481
00:45:05,828 --> 00:45:09,498
Bukan main lagi dia kutuk
hidup kita lebih bosan daripada dia.

482
00:45:10,374 --> 00:45:13,335
Ini memang lain macam punya perempuan.

483
00:45:13,419 --> 00:45:15,379
Selamba saja dia tipu kita.

484
00:45:15,462 --> 00:45:17,798
- Dah sedia nak mesyuarat?
- Kyeong-nam.

485
00:45:18,298 --> 00:45:21,135
So-yeong pun kena tempias juga, bukan?

486
00:45:21,218 --> 00:45:23,303
Cuba awak fikir.

487
00:45:23,387 --> 00:45:27,391
Kalau <i>DYPD </i>dibatalkan,
So-yeong hilang kerjalah nanti.

488
00:45:27,474 --> 00:45:29,435
Mungkin juga.

489
00:45:30,644 --> 00:45:32,896
Kita tak boleh biarkan. Tak boleh.

490
00:45:34,314 --> 00:45:35,149
Jangan.

491
00:45:35,232 --> 00:45:37,109
<i>So-yeong, awak okey?</i>

492
00:45:37,192 --> 00:45:41,196
<i>Kalau awak perlukan kerja baru,</i>
<i>saya akan carikan kerja yang bagus.</i>

493
00:45:41,280 --> 00:45:42,114
Jangan hantar.

494
00:45:42,197 --> 00:45:45,409
<i>Cik Yun tak pakai akalkah?</i>
<i>Sanggup dia aniaya awak?</i>

495
00:45:45,492 --> 00:45:47,745
<i>Balas mesej saya. Saya risaukan awak.</i>

496
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:55,252
<i>Dia tak aniaya saya. Faham?</i>

497
00:45:55,335 --> 00:45:58,422
<i>Saya pun pelanggan BoD.</i>
<i>Jangan nak menyibuk!</i>

498
00:45:58,505 --> 00:45:59,339
Apa?

499
00:46:00,090 --> 00:46:00,924
Kyeong-nam.

500
00:46:03,927 --> 00:46:06,013
Saya dah kata jangan hantar.

501
00:46:18,108 --> 00:46:18,942
Helo.

502
00:46:19,610 --> 00:46:20,694
<i>Awak dah makan?</i>

503
00:46:22,696 --> 00:46:23,530
Belum.

504
00:46:25,407 --> 00:46:26,533
Awak di mana?

505
00:46:26,617 --> 00:46:28,285
<i>Studio Cik Yun.</i>

506
00:46:28,786 --> 00:46:32,623
<i>So-yeong baru saja pergi,</i>
<i>tapi saya nak tunggu lagi.</i>

507
00:46:34,208 --> 00:46:36,460
Dia mungkin datang lambat.

508
00:46:39,505 --> 00:46:43,592
Kalau awak dah habis kerja,
boleh awak tolong saya?

509
00:46:43,675 --> 00:46:45,511
Boleh. Tolong apa?

510
00:46:46,011 --> 00:46:49,306
<i>Pemacu jari dengan nota mesyuarat</i>
<i>ada di rumah saya.</i>

511
00:46:49,389 --> 00:46:51,266
<i>Saya nak periksa sekarang.</i>

512
00:46:51,350 --> 00:46:54,144
Tapi saya risau Cik Yun balik
semasa saya tiada.

513
00:46:54,228 --> 00:46:59,107
Maaflah, tapi boleh awak pergi rumah saya
dan e-melkan kepada saya?

514
00:46:59,900 --> 00:47:01,735
Saya pergi sekarang.

515
00:47:01,819 --> 00:47:02,653
<i>Terima kasih.</i>

516
00:47:04,238 --> 00:47:06,406
Lambatlah saya balik nanti.

517
00:47:06,907 --> 00:47:09,076
Tapi boleh awak tunggu saya?

518
00:47:10,327 --> 00:47:12,412
Boleh. Jumpa nanti.

519
00:47:12,496 --> 00:47:13,413
<i>Jumpa nanti.</i>

520
00:47:40,065 --> 00:47:41,775
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

521
00:48:01,962 --> 00:48:03,422
Kenapa ada orang nak guna pun?

522
00:48:04,840 --> 00:48:06,091
ULASAN BOD

523
00:48:06,174 --> 00:48:08,677
TEMPOH PERCUBAAN: 50 JAM
TINJAUAN KEPUASAN

524
00:48:13,932 --> 00:48:14,766
Alamak.

525
00:48:32,993 --> 00:48:34,161
Aduh. Jawablah!

526
00:48:39,958 --> 00:48:41,376
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

527
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:45,589
Kenapa dia tak jawab?

528
00:48:51,595 --> 00:48:52,888
SEO MI-RAE

529
00:49:07,653 --> 00:49:09,112
Teksi!

530
00:49:12,282 --> 00:49:13,617
Saya nak ke Yongsan.

531
00:49:16,161 --> 00:49:17,829
Jawablah!

532
00:49:21,208 --> 00:49:22,626
8. ULASAN

533
00:49:40,227 --> 00:49:41,061
Tak guna.

534
00:49:48,568 --> 00:49:49,403
Mi-rae.

535
00:49:52,364 --> 00:49:53,198
Kenapa balik?

536
00:49:53,865 --> 00:49:55,742
Telefon awak…

537
00:49:56,243 --> 00:49:57,285
Kenapa tak jawab?

538
00:49:58,662 --> 00:49:59,997
Saya sibuk mengemas.

539
00:50:11,216 --> 00:50:12,050
Awak okey tak?

540
00:50:15,345 --> 00:50:16,346
Terima kasih.

541
00:50:21,727 --> 00:50:22,602
Ada yang tak kena?

542
00:50:24,438 --> 00:50:25,856
Ini sebab Cik Yun?

543
00:50:26,898 --> 00:50:27,899
Tak.

544
00:50:27,983 --> 00:50:29,693
Bos ada cakap apa-apa?

545
00:50:36,450 --> 00:50:38,535
Kenapa kelam-kabut balik? Risau saya.

546
00:50:43,290 --> 00:50:44,124
Saya cuma…

547
00:50:45,834 --> 00:50:47,085
Saya takut sangat.

548
00:50:48,837 --> 00:50:49,921
Takut apa?

549
00:50:53,467 --> 00:50:54,301
Takut…

550
00:50:55,635 --> 00:50:57,220
Takut segala-galanya.

551
00:51:07,314 --> 00:51:09,149
Mesti Cik Yun tak apa-apa.

552
00:51:11,818 --> 00:51:15,405
<i>Aku tak boleh beritahu dia</i>
<i>perkara yang menakutkan aku.</i>

553
00:51:16,364 --> 00:51:19,201
<i>Aku tak sanggup beritahu dia.</i>

554
00:52:38,155 --> 00:52:39,322
Ini gambar bila?

555
00:52:41,074 --> 00:52:42,325
Cantiknya dia.

556
00:52:47,539 --> 00:52:51,543
SAYA NAK CAKAP YANG SAYA SUKA AWAK

557
00:52:59,426 --> 00:53:00,927
<i>Saya bengang dengan awak.</i>

558
00:53:01,595 --> 00:53:04,598
<i>Sebab awak tak jawab pun</i>
<i>semasa saya ajak ikut saya.</i>

559
00:53:05,891 --> 00:53:08,643
<i>Saya ingat saya nak lupakan awak, tapi…</i>

560
00:53:09,895 --> 00:53:11,229
<i>Tapi susah betul.</i>

561
00:53:12,480 --> 00:53:13,565
<i>Saya rindu awak.</i>

562
00:54:14,918 --> 00:54:15,919
Seo Mi-rae.

563
00:54:36,606 --> 00:54:37,732
Kenapa baru datang?

564
00:54:39,067 --> 00:54:39,901
Apa?

565
00:54:43,613 --> 00:54:44,531
Mustahil…

566
00:58:04,856 --> 00:58:06,566
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

